*rasmol-2.7.2.1.1-r1 (15 Dec 2005)

  15 Dec 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  files/rasmol.sh.debian, +rasmol-2.7.2.1.1-r1.ebuild:
  Update rasmol script to fall back to xdpyinfo if xwininfo isn't available.
  Depend on one of the two.

  15 Dec 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  rasmol-2.7.2.1.1.ebuild:
  (#115649) Add rman to modular X deps.

  15 Dec 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  rasmol-2.7.2.1.1.ebuild:
  Add modular X dependencies.

  02 Jan 2005; Olivier Fisette <ribosome@gentoo.org> -rasmol-2.7.1.1.ebuild,
  rasmol-2.7.2.1.1.ebuild:
